* Debug build:
  cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Debug ../

* Find cmake build errors (best debugged with full compiler output):
  make VERBOSE=1

* Change c++ compiler:
  cmake ../ -DCMAKE_CXX_COMPILER=$HOME/lib/bin/g++

* smash binary is regularly checked by:
  valgrind -v ./smash
  
* smash src is checked by:
  cpplint.py *cc include/*h
  cppcheck --enable=all -I include/ .
